                "invention-title": [
                    "Small solid hydrogen storage device and use method",
                    "一种小型固态储氢装置及使用方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a small solid hydrogen storage device and a use method. The small solid hydrogen storage device comprises a solid hydrogen storage tank and a temperature control box, the solid hydrogen storage tank comprises a hydrogen storage module and a replaceable phase change material jacket module; the hydrogen storage module is used for adsorbing and storing hydrogen; the replaceable phase change material jacket module is used for providing heat for the hydrogen desorption process of the hydrogen storage module; the temperature control box is used for carrying out heating and heat preservation on the replaceable phase change material jacket module; the solid hydrogen storage tank realizes a hydrogenation process, a hydrogen desorption preheating process and a hydrogen desorption process through the temperature control box. Light weight and compactness of the device are facilitated, the phase change material can store or release energy in a phase change latent heat mode, the energy density of the phase change material is higher than that of sensible heat energy storage, and the heat absorption process is approximate to isothermal temperature and easy to control."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种小型固态储氢装置及使用方法，包括固态储氢罐和控温箱；所述固态储氢罐包括储氢模块和可替换的相变材料外套模块；所述储氢模块用于吸附并储存氢气；所述可替换的相变材料外套模块用于为储氢模块放氢过程提供热量；所述控温箱用于对可替换的相变材料外套模块进行加热和保温；所述固态储氢罐通过控温箱实现加氢过程、放氢预热过程和放氢过程。本发明有利于装置的轻量化和紧凑化，相变材料可以以相变潜热的方式储存或释放能量，且比显热储能的能量密度更高、吸热过程近似等温和过程易控制。"
                }
            ]
